creator: Chemical Applications
descriptionHtml: Vapour Pressures is an App designed to calculate vapour pressures and boiling points. It has two big databases and handles a large number of pressure and temperature units.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Version 2.0 is programmed entirely in Kotlin language, includes the following:

- New navigation menu
- New visual design
- Optimized performance
- It is possible to copy converted values to the clipboard.
